OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776402250
OL,3,CGovernment urged to ban concert ticket
OL,4,Cresale above face value 'without delay'
OL,6,FThe Government has been urged to ban
OL,7,Fthe resale of concert tickets above
OL,8,Fface value "without delay" as part of
OL,9,Fa review of live and electronic music
OL,10,Fcommissioned by the Culture, Media and
OL,11,FSport Committee.
OL,13,FThe report also prompted calls for a
OL,14,FGovernment and industry-backed Music
OL,15,FFan Association, similar to one set up
OL,16,Ffor football fans, and told it to
OL,17,Fcommit to a fans' charter made up of
OL,18,F50 recommendations to improve the live
OL,19,Fmusic industry.
OL,26,@pD@LOUpD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776402250
OL,3,CGovernment urged to ban concert ticket
OL,4,Cresale above face value 'without delay'
OL,6,FSpeaking at a launch event at the Le
OL,7,FPub live music venue in Newport, south
OL,8,FWales, review chairman Lord Brennan
OL,9,Fsaid: "Over the last year we've given
OL,10,Fa voice to fans of all different music
OL,11,Ftypes and genres from across the
OL,12,Fcountry, and they've told us loud and
OL,13,Fclear that often they feel neglected
OL,14,Fand ripped off.
OL,16,F"Sharp commercial practices and
OL,17,Fimpersonal service are now all too
OL,18,Fprevalent in the music world and point
OL,19,Fto an industry that fails to treat its
OL,20,Ffans, the lifeblood of the sector,
OL,21,Fwith respect.
OL,26,@qD@GOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776402250
OL,3,CGovernment urged to ban concert ticket
OL,4,Cresale above face value 'without delay'
OL,6,F"Our new fans' charter sets out a
OL,7,Fpractical and achievable way ahead
OL,8,Fthat everyone, from ticketing
OL,9,Fplatforms to venues, from artists to
OL,10,Fpromoters, from managers to councils,
OL,11,Fcan sign up to, to help secure the
OL,12,Flong-term future of live music.
OL,14,F"From establishing a proper
OL,15,Frepresentative body to give fans more
OL,16,Fclout and ending the ticketing rip-
OL,17,Foff, to improving access for disabled
OL,18,Fgig goers and venue safety, it's time
OL,19,Ffor all involved in music to turn the
OL,20,Fvolume dial up to 11 in favour of the
OL,21,Ffans."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU}D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776402250
OL,3,CGovernment urged to ban concert ticket
OL,4,Cresale above face value 'without delay'
OL,6,FRecommendations in the charter include
OL,7,Fthat the Government ensures tiered
OL,8,Fticket pricing is "clearly
OL,9,Fcommunicated in advance and applied
OL,10,Ftransparently", and that the industry
OL,11,Fcontinues to "resist the introduction
OL,12,Fof dynamic surge pricing".
OL,14,FThe report read: "Fans across the
OL,15,Freview had a negative perception... of
OL,16,Fmajor online ticketing platforms. They
OL,17,Ffelt that the big agencies did not
OL,18,Ftreat fans fairly, that ticket prices
OL,19,Fwere too high, and that little was
OL,20,Fbeing done to deal with bots and
OL,21,Fonline ticket touts."
OL,26,@pD@SOUrD@NO]sD@NOUtD@YO]vD@ROU}D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776402250
OL,3,CGovernment urged to ban concert ticket
OL,4,Cresale above face value 'without delay'
OL,6,FA survey conducted as part of the
OL,7,Freview found changing ticket prices
OL,8,Fled to fans feeling "heightened levels
OL,9,Fof stress, fear of missing out and
OL,10,Fpressure to make unaffordable
OL,11,Fdecisions".
OL,13,FIt also said the Government should
OL,14,Finsist on "clear, upfront information"
OL,15,Ffrom sellers on ticket refund
OL,16,Fpolicies, introduce a mandatory levy
OL,17,Fon larger events to benefit grassroots
OL,18,Fvenues, festivals, promoters, and
OL,19,Fupcoming artists; while venues should
OL,20,Fbe required to provide free earplugs
OL,21,Fand drinking water.
OL,26,@pD@UOUsD@JO]vD@KOUvD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776402250
OL,3,CGovernment urged to ban concert ticket
OL,4,Cresale above face value 'without delay'
OL,6,FVenues were also told they should
OL,7,Fpublish clear start and finish times
OL,8,Ffor sets as standard to ensure fans
OL,9,Fare able to plan their journeys to and
OL,10,Ffrom concerts in advance, and the
OL,11,Freview told promoters and venues to
OL,12,Fexplore the demand for daytime live
OL,13,Fmusic events.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776402250
OL,3,CGovernment urged to ban concert ticket
OL,4,Cresale above face value 'without delay'
OL,6,FThe review said venues should work
OL,7,Ftowards allocating a minimum of 2% of
OL,8,Ftheir total capacity to wheelchair
OL,9,Faccessible spaces, called for fans and
OL,10,Fvenues to establish a code of conduct
OL,11,Ffor behaviour at gigs, and told the
OL,12,FGovernment to establish an annual,
OL,13,Frotating live music roadshow.
OL,15,FIt said the Government should
OL,16,Fcommission an annual music fans'
OL,17,Fsurvey from 2027 to provide ministers,
OL,18,Findustry and other stakeholders with
OL,19,Fregular insight into live and
OL,20,Felectronic music fans.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776402250
OL,3,CGovernment urged to ban concert ticket
OL,4,Cresale above face value 'without delay'
OL,6,FA DCMS spokesperson said in response
OL,7,Fto the review: "We thank the committee
OL,8,Ffor their report and will consider its
OL,9,Ffindings carefully.
OL,11,F"The Government shares the ambition of
OL,12,Fthe committee to ensure that live
OL,13,Fmusic and its fans thrive in the UK.
OL,14,FWe will soon publish a Music Plan,
OL,15,Fdrawing together all that Government
OL,16,Fis doing to support the music
OL,17,Findustry, including a #30 million
OL,18,FMusic Growth Package to support
OL,19,Fdomestic growth, talent development
OL,20,Fand music exports.
OL,26,@oD@POUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776402250
OL,3,CGovernment urged to ban concert ticket
OL,4,Cresale above face value 'without delay'
OL,6,F"We set out decisive plans last year
OL,7,Fto stamp out touting once and for all,
OL,8,Fand we are committed to delivering on
OL,9,Fthese as soon as possible for the
OL,10,Fbenefit of fans and industry."
OL,12,FThe review was one of the
OL,13,Frecommendations from the committee's
OL,14,Freport on grassroots music venues,
OL,15,Fwhich raised the concerns of venue
OL,16,Foperators, touring artists and
OL,17,Findependent promoters regarding the
OL,18,Ffinancial state of the grassroots
OL,19,Fmusic sector.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776402250
OL,3,CGovernment urged to ban concert ticket
OL,4,Cresale above face value 'without delay'
OL,6,FWhen the Government did not take up
OL,7,Fthe recommendations of the report, the
OL,8,Fcommittee asked Lord Brennan to
OL,9,Fconduct the independent review, which
OL,10,Ftook on the views of thousands of
OL,11,Fmusic fans through a national survey
OL,12,Fand nationwide engagement events.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
